<br>
In this, the Ratns Forum of XSB (henceforth known to be xevserverboards) the poster does have the right to post anyting (s)he may want to post.  With that right will be responsibilities, MAINLY those to keep your (the poster's) post in accordance to a few simple rules.<br>
<br>
(1) Do not spam<br>
(2) Refarin from direct posting of porn or anything a normaly employed person would be under suspicion at work for posting.  Links may be allowable, but you (the poster) will hve to use your discretion.<br>
*note* yes, normaly employed is a subjective term.  If you (the poster) have questions about it, then the material is probably pornopgraphic and should NOT be posted.  A link to the material might be allowable, but once again, if you (the poster) question the nature of this being too vulgar, it should probably NOT be posted.<br>
<br>
Now, PERHAPS I fucked this all up (not being a mod and all) and the rules are nothing like this.  Maybe porn is completely allowable now, and spam is fine.  If you (the poster) want to make them off-limits, you (the poster) will have to go to the mod forum and take it up with the moderators there.  Phrases like &quot;OMG U R Teh suxxorz!  U R 2 allow my pics prz.. kk thx prz pst&quot; will probably be deleted and you (the poster) will be ignored.  In rants, however, you you (the poster), will just be ignored.  Unlike rants, you (the poster) will have to conduct yourself (the poster's self) like someone (a poster) that has a legitimate concern and should be listened to.<br>
<br>
We (the xev posters) can think of some people that are incapable of this (Wrin, Crylin), and this is a way of just cutting the bullshit out and letting a forum exist where problems can be discussed without the constant &quot;Off my nutsack, bitch&quot; and &quot;You broke rule 93749 clause a3 subclause iii part 2.&quot; <br>
<br>
did that clear it up some?<br>
<br>
I don't know if it was needed or not, since I think this board is fine as it is.  Sure, some people are annoying pieces of monkey shit, but rants are fine for people like Crylin.  They aren't the ONLY people in this forum, and CERTIANLY not on this board.  Considering how many people come to rants to just bitch, I think it is a good idea to give people with legitimite gripes a place to air them that is NOT here.  Think about it (Wrin), if you (Wrin) think the mods are just going to blow you (Wrin) off, you (Wrin) probably didn't have anything worth saying anyway. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub228.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tibult>tibult</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www-personal.umich.edu/~nnettles/Nick1.gif" BORDER=0> at: 12/4/03 1:42 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=1188.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=1188.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=1188.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=1188.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=1188.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1188.topic&index=64><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=1188.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/